{
  "design_notes": "A cohesive medium-difficulty chart designed to emphasize the intense drops while maintaining a clean, easily-readable foot flow. The intro introduces the player to syncopated taps and eighth-note jumps. S1 initiates a solid stream of taps mixed with well-spaced holds. S3 builds upon S1 with comfortable zigzag movement. S4 represents the peak density drop where we introduce dense streams in box patterns but keep them clean of tricky crossovers. S5 serves as a breather section before S6's final energy burst, resolving into a fading outro to prevent empty charting space.",
